@startuml
actor "Партнер-лидер" as Partner
actor "Бизнес-менеджер" as Manager
participant "Web shell" as Frontend
participant "mlm-structure API" as MLM
participant "partner-reporting" as Reports
participant "bonus-wallet" as Bonus
participant "order" as Order
Partner -> Frontend: open /business
Frontend -> MLM: GET /api/mlm-structure/dashboard?campaignId=CAT-2026-05
MLM --> Frontend: MlmDashboardResponse + STR_MNEMO_MLM_STRUCTURE_DASHBOARD_READY
Partner -> Frontend: open /business/beauty-community
Frontend -> MLM: GET /api/mlm-structure/community
MLM --> Frontend: Downline levels and branches
Manager -> Frontend: open /business/conversion
Frontend -> MLM: GET /api/mlm-structure/conversion
MLM --> Frontend: Invite funnel
Partner -> Frontend: open /business/partner-card/BOG-016-002
Frontend -> MLM: GET /api/mlm-structure/partners/BOG-016-002
MLM -> Order: links to order history route
MLM -> Bonus: links to bonus wallet route
MLM -> Reports: links to partner report route
MLM --> Frontend: Partner card with linkedActions
@enduml